1
00:01:43,437 --> 00:01:44,304
Hello?

2
00:01:44,638 --> 00:01:47,074
Huaze Lei, why did you call me?

3
00:01:47,441 --> 00:01:49,443
Because I saw a frustrated lady
in front of me.

4
00:01:49,876 --> 00:01:52,613
I feel sorry for her,
so I want to treat her to a cup of coffee.

5
00:01:53,413 --> 00:01:54,615
Frustrated lady?

6
00:01:58,986 --> 00:02:00,587
Please mind your words,

7
00:02:00,654 --> 00:02:03,457
or there will be no pretty lady
drinking coffee with you.

8
00:02:14,635 --> 00:02:16,103
Every time we get to this season,

9
00:02:16,603 --> 00:02:18,271
I enjoy wandering around the streets.

10
00:02:19,239 --> 00:02:21,375
I was looking for a coffee shop
to have a cup of coffee,

11
00:02:22,042 --> 00:02:23,076
then I saw you.

12
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:29,950
You often wander around by yourself
and drink coffee alone.

13
00:02:30,417 --> 00:02:31,585
Don't you feel lonely?

14
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,855
Only frustrated people feel lonely.

15
00:02:35,756 --> 00:02:37,624
Don't try to imply things, okay?

16
00:02:38,191 --> 00:02:39,993
I've already thought it through.

17
00:02:49,403 --> 00:02:51,571
<i>We also went out on a date before.</i>

18
00:02:51,638 --> 00:02:53,674
<i>It would've been nice if we were able
to chat naturally</i>

19
00:02:53,740 --> 00:02:55,275
<i>like what we're doing now.</i>

20
00:03:00,447 --> 00:03:01,381
What's the matter?

21
00:03:02,816 --> 00:03:05,519
Nothing. I just think
the atmosphere is nice.

22
00:03:05,585 --> 00:03:06,753
I feel comfortable.

23
00:03:07,821 --> 00:03:08,689
Yeah.

24
00:03:10,557 --> 00:03:13,360
I really want to soak in hot springs
in this type of weather.

25
00:03:13,427 --> 00:03:15,529
You want to soak in hot springs
in such a hot day?

26
00:03:15,996 --> 00:03:17,964
You took me to fly a kite
when it was raining last time.

27
00:03:18,031 --> 00:03:19,733
You're so weird.

28
00:03:24,438 --> 00:03:25,405
Shancai.

29
00:03:26,006 --> 00:03:27,074
What a coincidence.

30
00:03:27,507 --> 00:03:29,376
Yeah, what a coincidence.

31
00:03:29,810 --> 00:03:31,111
Have you been here long?

32
00:03:31,178 --> 00:03:32,546
Yeah, we've been here for a while.

33
00:03:36,049 --> 00:03:37,918
Who is he? Are you on a date?

34
00:03:38,618 --> 00:03:41,388
No, he's Huaze Lei.
We just met by accident.

35
00:03:41,655 --> 00:03:43,056
So you're Huaze Lei.

36
00:03:43,123 --> 00:03:45,525
Hi, I'm Ah Si's fiancee.
My name is Xiaozi.

37
00:03:46,126 --> 00:03:47,394
Can we sit with you?

38
00:03:49,463 --> 00:03:51,732
Who sits this way on a date?
Come and sit together.

39
00:03:52,733 --> 00:03:53,767
Come on.

40
00:03:53,834 --> 00:03:54,701
Hurry.

41
00:03:56,002 --> 00:03:57,938
Don't just stand there. Come and sit down.

42
00:03:58,438 --> 00:03:59,506
Have a seat.

43
00:04:02,809 --> 00:04:03,744
Are you on a date?

44
00:04:03,810 --> 00:04:04,678
Yes.

45
00:04:05,011 --> 00:04:07,047
It looks like everything is going well.

46
00:04:08,281 --> 00:04:10,250
Yes, look at us sitting together.

47
00:04:10,317 --> 00:04:12,586
It's like two couples on a double date.

48
00:04:12,853 --> 00:04:14,254
Yes, it looks like it.

49
00:04:14,588 --> 00:04:15,756
Stop talking nonsense.

50
00:04:16,523 --> 00:04:17,858
Why are you so mad?

51
00:04:18,258 --> 00:04:20,627
I'm sorry. He's feeling embarrassed
so he's acting tough.

52
00:04:20,961 --> 00:04:23,296
That's okay. We've been used to it.

53
00:04:23,363 --> 00:04:24,765
He behaved like this just now.

54
00:04:24,831 --> 00:04:27,067
He kept saying he was bored
and wanted to go home.

55
00:04:27,134 --> 00:04:30,036
So I thought we should go to a hotel,
but he tried to run away.

56
00:04:32,072 --> 00:04:33,940
Don't you think your relationship
is moving too fast?

57
00:04:34,007 --> 00:04:37,544
No. After all, we've already kissed,
so I think we can move to the next stage.

58
00:04:37,611 --> 00:04:39,679
Stop talking too much, will you?

59
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,281
What's the matter?

60
00:04:41,348 --> 00:04:42,916
Your girlfriend has done so much for you.

61
00:04:42,983 --> 00:04:44,417
You should be thankful.

62
00:04:44,818 --> 00:04:47,554
A good man shouldn't let a girl down.

63
00:04:47,621 --> 00:04:48,722
That's what I'm talking about.

64
00:04:50,257 --> 00:04:52,959
I tell you what, my family has
a vacation mansion on the hill.

65
00:04:53,026 --> 00:04:55,295
School is off tomorrow anyway.
Let's go together, shall we?

66
00:04:57,030 --> 00:04:59,065
No, you two can go without us.

67
00:04:59,132 --> 00:05:01,601
Huaze Lei and I will be two third wheels,
so it's going to be so weird.

68
00:05:01,668 --> 00:05:02,669
Right, Huaze Lei?

69
00:05:02,936 --> 00:05:03,804
Is there a hot spring?

70
00:05:03,870 --> 00:05:06,139
Yes, so you're into hot springs?

71
00:05:06,206 --> 00:05:08,241
What a coincidence.
Our hot spring is pretty good.

72
00:05:08,942 --> 00:05:10,744
Really? Fine, I'll go.

73
00:05:11,278 --> 00:05:12,379
Great. Let's all go together.

74
00:05:22,956 --> 00:05:23,790
Ma'am.

75
00:05:24,191 --> 00:05:25,292
Anything new?

76
00:05:26,226 --> 00:05:27,127
Ma'am,

77
00:05:27,561 --> 00:05:30,964
Young Master and Miss Xiaozi
went into Miss Xiaozi's mansion.

78
00:05:31,565 --> 00:05:34,568
My man saw them go in there together.

79
00:05:35,202 --> 00:05:39,005
In this situation, they will spend a night
in the mansion tonight.

80
00:05:42,175 --> 00:05:43,944
Xiaozi is a smart kid.

81
00:05:44,444 --> 00:05:45,912
She learned what I taught her very well.

82
00:05:47,314 --> 00:05:50,684
But Young Master Huaze and Miss Shancai

83
00:05:50,750 --> 00:05:52,052
went with them.

84
00:05:55,822 --> 00:05:57,924
What? What's going on?

85
00:05:58,525 --> 00:06:01,194
The four of them met in a cafÃ©.

86
00:06:02,062 --> 00:06:05,665
I don't know how, but they went
to Miss Xiaozi's mansion together.

87
00:06:07,234 --> 00:06:10,237
That poor woman Shancai
keeps lingering around them.

88
00:06:10,837 --> 00:06:12,372
What is she up to this time?

89
00:06:14,507 --> 00:06:15,408
Wait.

90
00:06:16,610 --> 00:06:19,880
You said she was with Huaze Lei before.

91
00:06:20,213 --> 00:06:21,615
Then the four of them went together?

92
00:06:21,681 --> 00:06:22,515
Yes.

93
00:06:24,818 --> 00:06:27,420
Could it be that she gave up Ah Si

94
00:06:27,954 --> 00:06:30,557
and went back to pursue Huaze Lei?

95
00:06:32,259 --> 00:06:33,560
This is good.

96
00:06:34,194 --> 00:06:37,998
After tonight, Ah Si and Xiaozi
will get into a serious relationship.

97
00:06:38,932 --> 00:06:40,901
She will give up then, right?

98
00:07:00,420 --> 00:07:01,655
It's so comfortable.

99
00:07:03,623 --> 00:07:05,358
Shancai, what's the matter?

100
00:07:05,425 --> 00:07:07,227
Why are you so lifeless?

101
00:07:07,761 --> 00:07:12,599
No, I'm just thinking your mansion
is awesome.

102
00:07:12,666 --> 00:07:15,201
Really? I think it's not bad.

103
00:07:15,602 --> 00:07:19,139
But the house is kind of old,
and the rooms are a little small.

104
00:07:19,806 --> 00:07:22,008
But it's still pretty good
when I come here every now and then.

105
00:07:24,511 --> 00:07:25,578
Xiaozi.

106
00:07:26,079 --> 00:07:29,316
It's great that you are
in a serious relationship with Daoming Si.

107
00:07:29,382 --> 00:07:32,719
Do you think so?
I'm feeling kind of happy, too.

108
00:07:33,954 --> 00:07:35,789
-Great.
-Thanks.

109
00:07:37,791 --> 00:07:41,728
<i>No, I don't think it's great. I'm hurt.</i>

110
00:07:42,329 --> 00:07:44,631
<i>Since I saw them kissed,</i>

111
00:07:45,198 --> 00:07:47,567
<i>there's a wound on my heart.</i>

112
00:07:48,501 --> 00:07:52,672
<i>Daoming Si's love is so strong
and so heavy</i>

113
00:07:52,739 --> 00:07:54,674
<i>that I feel like I can't breathe anymore.</i>

114
00:07:56,543 --> 00:07:58,678
I don't know what other couples are like,

115
00:07:58,745 --> 00:08:00,647
but I keep telling myself

116
00:08:00,714 --> 00:08:03,116
not to treat Ah Si like a normal boy.

117
00:08:03,183 --> 00:08:05,852
Otherwise, I will think that
he doesn't love me enough.

118
00:08:06,519 --> 00:08:09,022
Sometimes his indifference makes me mad,

119
00:08:09,556 --> 00:08:12,292
but when I speak out what I think,
he's willing to cooperate with me.

120
00:08:12,359 --> 00:08:13,693
<i>If you run away,</i>

121
00:08:15,261 --> 00:08:16,429
I'll chase after you.

122
00:08:17,564 --> 00:08:18,898
No matter where you are,

123
00:08:19,432 --> 00:08:20,900
even if you're in hell,

124
00:08:22,369 --> 00:08:24,104
No matter which corner
of the world you're in,

125
00:08:25,572 --> 00:08:26,906
I'll chase you down.

126
00:08:28,441 --> 00:08:31,277
<i>I thought I could put an end to it
this time,</i>

127
00:08:31,344 --> 00:08:32,879
<i>and run away from him.</i>

128
00:08:33,213 --> 00:08:37,317
<i>But why does it seem that I'm getting
sucked into a bigger vortex</i>

129
00:08:37,851 --> 00:08:40,754
<i>with a wound hurting like hell
on my heart?</i>

130
00:08:43,790 --> 00:08:45,558
Well, that's fine.

131
00:08:46,059 --> 00:08:47,660
I don't have to compare with others.

132
00:08:47,727 --> 00:08:49,829
I believe our relationship
will get better.

133
00:08:50,830 --> 00:08:53,633
If he won't take the initiative, I will.

134
00:08:54,334 --> 00:08:56,970
I even hope we can move
into the next stage tonight.

135
00:08:57,837 --> 00:08:58,705
Shancai!

136
00:08:58,772 --> 00:09:02,409
Is there anyone outside?
Come in and help us!

137
00:09:05,245 --> 00:09:06,079
What happened?

138
00:09:06,146 --> 00:09:08,481
Shancai fainted in the hot spring,
and I can't carry her.

139
00:09:24,397 --> 00:09:26,533
Maybe she's been in there for too long
so she fainted.

140
00:09:27,133 --> 00:09:28,568
I think she'll be fine.

141
00:09:29,936 --> 00:09:30,804
Xiaozi.

142
00:09:31,638 --> 00:09:33,006
Take her back to her room.

143
00:09:33,473 --> 00:09:34,974
Oh, follow me.

144
00:10:18,785 --> 00:10:20,086
Here, drink some water.

145
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:21,454
Thank you.

146
00:10:25,859 --> 00:10:26,860
What happened to me?

147
00:10:26,926 --> 00:10:29,262
You've been in the hot spring for too long
so you fainted.

148
00:10:30,730 --> 00:10:32,465
Huaze Lei, did you save me?

149
00:10:33,533 --> 00:10:34,968
So you saw everything, right?

150
00:10:35,735 --> 00:10:37,971
Didn't I already put your robe on?

151
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:42,575
So you saw everything
when you were putting my robe on?

152
00:10:42,642 --> 00:10:43,610
Yes.

153
00:10:44,544 --> 00:10:45,678
I saw you,

154
00:10:45,745 --> 00:10:48,381
but what else could I do
in that situation?

155
00:10:49,616 --> 00:10:52,719
Yeah, right. But still, you're a guy.

156
00:10:53,119 --> 00:10:55,054
Why didn't you get a girl to save me?

157
00:10:55,655 --> 00:10:58,691
-Where's Xiaozi?
-She might be sleeping now.

158
00:10:59,025 --> 00:11:01,528
Ah Si is in the same room with her.
And we are sharing this room.

159
00:11:02,262 --> 00:11:04,664
Why should we sleep in the same room?
There are enough rooms for us.

160
00:11:04,731 --> 00:11:06,366
-I'll talk to her.
-Hey, stop.

161
00:11:06,799 --> 00:11:08,568
I don't think you should disturb them.

162
00:11:09,035 --> 00:11:10,904
Maybe they're doing it now.

163
00:11:11,971 --> 00:11:13,072
Doing it?

164
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:15,141
Are they?

165
00:11:16,176 --> 00:11:18,378
Oh, right, silly me.

166
00:11:19,913 --> 00:11:21,648
You can stop them if you want.

167
00:11:22,448 --> 00:11:24,117
Should I smash down their door for you?

168
00:11:25,652 --> 00:11:27,387
Why would I stop them?

169
00:11:29,422 --> 00:11:30,924
Because since you came here,

170
00:11:31,791 --> 00:11:33,726
you're about to cry.

171
00:11:37,130 --> 00:11:39,766
Huaze Lei, why did you agree to come here?

172
00:11:40,533 --> 00:11:43,403
Didn't you say we shouldn't get things
more complicated?

173
00:11:44,404 --> 00:11:45,905
Then why are we here?

174
00:11:47,140 --> 00:11:50,643
I think we shouldn't avoid
what is meant to happen.

175
00:11:51,811 --> 00:11:54,080
We met at the coffee shop,

176
00:11:55,048 --> 00:11:56,883
so do we have to pretend
we can't see each other?

177
00:11:58,151 --> 00:12:01,120
Maybe this is a chance

178
00:12:02,021 --> 00:12:05,592
for everybody to either
make things clearer or more confusing.

179
00:12:07,560 --> 00:12:10,330
<i>If I could, I would rather become blind.</i>

180
00:12:30,283 --> 00:12:31,184
Ah Si.

181
00:12:32,385 --> 00:12:35,255
My mom said I'll live at your place
in the next semester.

182
00:12:35,755 --> 00:12:39,325
I'll be learning how to be a good wife
in the following days.

183
00:12:41,127 --> 00:12:43,563
If you think four years in college
is too long,

184
00:12:43,630 --> 00:12:46,132
it's okay if you choose to marry
before graduation.

185
00:13:00,013 --> 00:13:01,314
Do you agree with this?

186
00:13:03,483 --> 00:13:05,785
Are you satisfied with the decision
your parents made for you?

187
00:13:09,589 --> 00:13:11,524
Of course, it's not my place
to criticize you.

188
00:13:15,128 --> 00:13:17,530
Apparently, your future
has been decided, hasn't it?

189
00:13:18,064 --> 00:13:21,434
You mean, you want to decide
who you'll love?

190
00:13:25,838 --> 00:13:27,774
Didn't you already decide
that I'm the one?

191
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:29,575
Why are you asking so many questions?

192
00:13:38,551 --> 00:13:39,452
Fine.

193
00:13:40,486 --> 00:13:42,422
If you aren't going to answer,
I won't ask anymore.

194
00:13:44,490 --> 00:13:47,460
But please look at me right now.

195
00:13:57,070 --> 00:14:00,340
<i>I must stop going back and forth
about my feelings towards Daoming Si.</i>

196
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:03,476
<i>Can I rush into their room?</i>

197
00:14:04,010 --> 00:14:06,346
<i>Of course, I can't. Absolutely can't.</i>

198
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:12,352
<i>But an inexplicable pain
is gripping my heart.</i>

199
00:14:15,254 --> 00:14:17,590
Huaze Lei, are you sleeping now?

200
00:14:19,258 --> 00:14:20,326
Not yet.

201
00:14:22,128 --> 00:14:24,664
Why did they only give us one blanket?

202
00:14:26,165 --> 00:14:27,433
Does it matter?

203
00:14:28,267 --> 00:14:29,669
It's warmer this way.

204
00:14:30,136 --> 00:14:33,039
And this room is so cold.

205
00:14:36,876 --> 00:14:38,978
Could I hold your hand?

206
00:14:45,485 --> 00:14:46,452
Yes.

207
00:14:53,359 --> 00:14:56,095
<i>Tonight, there's one more wound
on my heart.</i>

208
00:14:56,562 --> 00:15:00,466
<i>Maybe the one who can heal the wound
is Huaze Lei.</i>

209
00:15:01,067 --> 00:15:04,804
<i>He's beside me,
so I'm not that lonely now.</i>

210
00:15:06,873 --> 00:15:08,508
Huaze Lei, thank you.

211
00:15:09,509 --> 00:15:10,576
For what?

212
00:15:13,479 --> 00:15:16,215
Thank you for saving me in the hot spring.

213
00:15:16,949 --> 00:15:18,284
It just happened this way.

214
00:15:18,918 --> 00:15:22,388
The moment I finished shower,
I heard Xiaozi yelling that you fainted.

215
00:15:23,156 --> 00:15:24,824
She's so impetuous.

216
00:15:25,625 --> 00:15:26,893
And fierce.

217
00:15:27,627 --> 00:15:29,562
I've met many girls
who are from rich families.

218
00:15:29,629 --> 00:15:31,564
I haven't met her type of girls before.

219
00:15:32,765 --> 00:15:36,803
Yeah, but I think she's pretty cute.
I like her.

220
00:15:37,236 --> 00:15:40,673
She is so reckless that she always
makes people so nervous.

221
00:15:42,208 --> 00:15:47,146
But I think she's a girl
with both maturity and willfulness,

222
00:15:47,213 --> 00:15:49,182
so you won't hate her.

223
00:15:49,615 --> 00:15:52,051
She's just like Daoming Si in some ways.

224
00:15:52,118 --> 00:15:55,221
She's not exactly like Ah Si.

225
00:15:57,056 --> 00:15:59,659
No one can match his willfulness
after all.

226
00:16:00,426 --> 00:16:01,394
Yeah.

227
00:16:02,428 --> 00:16:03,729
You finally smiled.

228
00:16:04,397 --> 00:16:06,399
-I didn't smile before?
-You don't think so?

229
00:16:07,333 --> 00:16:10,002
You've been putting
on a grumpy face the whole day.

230
00:16:10,636 --> 00:16:12,972
I've been putting on this face
since I enrolled in Yingde.

231
00:16:13,039 --> 00:16:15,041
I've been like this for a long time.

232
00:16:15,107 --> 00:16:16,576
You are bickering with me now.

233
00:16:17,443 --> 00:16:19,178
This is the Shancai I know.

234
00:16:19,846 --> 00:16:21,981
You were so frustrated just now.

235
00:16:23,015 --> 00:16:24,183
Shut up.

236
00:16:24,984 --> 00:16:29,155
Fine. You can vent
all your problems on me.

237
00:16:29,222 --> 00:16:32,058
I don't have any problems.
Besides, why should I vent on you?

238
00:16:32,124 --> 00:16:35,161
You don't? You've already thrown
two pillows, miss.

239
00:16:35,228 --> 00:16:38,364
Fine, I'll throw a third one. You still...

240
00:16:39,599 --> 00:16:42,668
<i>I feel like I'm on the rooftop.</i>

241
00:16:43,035 --> 00:16:45,037
<i>When I'm at my worst times,</i>

242
00:16:45,338 --> 00:16:48,441
<i>Lei will always be blowing a gentle wind
to my heart.</i>

243
00:16:48,508 --> 00:16:51,043
<i>I no longer feel heartbroken
at the thought of him,</i>

244
00:16:51,511 --> 00:16:54,447
<i>and my feeling towards him
is not love anymore.</i>

245
00:16:54,914 --> 00:16:58,851
<i>But I know I'll like Huaze Lei forever.</i>

246
00:16:58,918 --> 00:17:00,453
Come here. Hey!

247
00:17:01,153 --> 00:17:02,855
-Hey.
-I'm tired now. Stop.

248
00:17:08,861 --> 00:17:10,196
Put your clothes on.

249
00:17:11,931 --> 00:17:12,899
Why?

250
00:17:13,799 --> 00:17:15,635
Why can you say it so calmly?

251
00:17:16,669 --> 00:17:18,804
It may seem like
