00:34:57,462 --> 00:35:00,932
-Why did you come here so late?
-Oh, I have something to tell you.

505
00:35:01,766 --> 00:35:03,268
-Something to tell me?
-Yeah.

506
00:35:04,002 --> 00:35:07,772
<i>Is she about to tell me about
her making out with Daoming Si?</i>

507
00:35:08,340 --> 00:35:11,009
-It's--
-I'm sorry, I don't want to hear it.

508
00:35:18,450 --> 00:35:22,420
Xiaozi, didn't you find it weird
that I'm the only one home?

509
00:35:22,487 --> 00:35:23,888
Yeah, a little.

510
00:35:24,289 --> 00:35:26,591
It's because my parents have moved away.

511
00:35:26,658 --> 00:35:29,260
From today, I'll be living alone.

512
00:35:29,694 --> 00:35:32,163
I think it's something new
and I'm very nervous.

513
00:35:32,230 --> 00:35:35,967
Really? Your parents won't be watching
your every move. You're free now.

514
00:35:36,034 --> 00:35:38,803
Yeah, so from now on,

515
00:35:38,870 --> 00:35:41,740
I have to take care of everything
in my life.

516
00:35:42,741 --> 00:35:47,779
So I have no time to think
about other things.

517
00:35:50,548 --> 00:35:53,952
If you want to talk with me
about something,

518
00:35:54,919 --> 00:35:56,755
I might not be able
to give you advice anymore.

519
00:35:58,323 --> 00:36:00,892
Shancai, do you hate me?

520
00:36:01,493 --> 00:36:03,795
No, it's not what you think.

521
00:36:03,862 --> 00:36:04,996
I didn't mean that.

522
00:36:06,364 --> 00:36:09,334
If you hate me, I can understand.

523
00:36:11,569 --> 00:36:12,671
I lied to you.

524
00:36:14,172 --> 00:36:15,674
Maybe because I envy you,

525
00:36:16,441 --> 00:36:17,742
that's why I did not tell you.

526
00:36:19,110 --> 00:36:22,013
Actually, nothing happened that night.

527
00:36:22,747 --> 00:36:25,550
Ah Si told me that he couldn't be with me,

528
00:36:25,884 --> 00:36:27,786
so nothing happened between us.

529
00:36:28,920 --> 00:36:31,189
I was pretty satisfied with my body,

530
00:36:31,256 --> 00:36:33,925
and I thought if I took off my clothes,
he would...

531
00:36:34,492 --> 00:36:37,729
You know, he would go weak in the knees
or be attracted to me or something.

532
00:36:38,096 --> 00:36:40,231
So I just took off all my clothes.

533
00:36:40,298 --> 00:36:43,201
I couldn't believe he didn't even move
a muscle. He didn't show me any respect.

534
00:36:45,036 --> 00:36:46,938
That was a huge humiliation for a woman.

535
00:36:50,842 --> 00:36:56,715
Today, I've told my mother to go
to Ah Si's house to cancel the engagement.

536
00:36:57,749 --> 00:37:00,952
Why? I thought things were going well
between you two.

537
00:37:03,421 --> 00:37:05,356
Although things didn't end up well
between Ah Si and me,

538
00:37:05,423 --> 00:37:07,859
I still hope we can still be friends.

539
00:37:09,427 --> 00:37:11,496
I came here today to say this to you.

540
00:37:12,464 --> 00:37:16,468
Through my engagement
with Daoming Si, I met you,

541
00:37:16,968 --> 00:37:19,838
and I became friends with you.
I'm so happy.

542
00:37:24,275 --> 00:37:27,345
Sorry, I'm having an allergic reaction.
Why does my nose keep running?

543
00:37:31,716 --> 00:37:34,219
<i>I just told those harsh words to her.</i>

544
00:37:35,186 --> 00:37:37,856
<i>Sometimes, I find Xiaozi annoying.</i>

545
00:37:38,423 --> 00:37:40,191
<i>I think she can feel it, too.</i>

546
00:37:40,859 --> 00:37:44,796
<i>But she came here so late at night,
just to tell me this.</i>

547
00:37:46,297 --> 00:37:47,532
Sorry, I'm leaving now.

548
00:37:48,166 --> 00:37:49,067
Xiaozi.

549
00:37:49,934 --> 00:37:51,469
If you don't mind,

550
00:37:52,170 --> 00:37:53,872
I want to be your friend forever.

551
00:38:00,645 --> 00:38:02,380
I'll be rooting for you forever.

552
00:38:02,747 --> 00:38:04,983
I won't bring you any problems anymore.

553
00:38:05,517 --> 00:38:06,618
Xiaozi.

554
00:38:06,684 --> 00:38:07,786
Listen to me.

555
00:38:08,153 --> 00:38:10,355
If you really consider me as your friend,

556
00:38:11,256 --> 00:38:14,292
stop caring about how I feel
and lying to yourself.

557
00:38:15,827 --> 00:38:16,928
I didn't.

558
00:38:17,662 --> 00:38:19,063
I'm leaving now. Bye-bye.

559
00:38:22,634 --> 00:38:23,902
I forgot to tell you.

560
00:38:25,003 --> 00:38:29,107
Ah Si rejected me because he said
all he can think about is you.

561
00:38:38,316 --> 00:38:40,218
I saw the four of them went--

562
00:38:44,956 --> 00:38:45,857
Young Master.

563
00:38:49,093 --> 00:38:50,595
My son came home.

564
00:38:52,664 --> 00:38:55,366
Tell the cook to prepare dinner for Ah Si.

565
00:38:55,433 --> 00:38:56,301
Yes.

566
00:38:56,601 --> 00:38:58,937
Don't bother. I'm not hungry.

567
00:38:59,704 --> 00:39:00,939
I have something to tell you.

568
00:39:02,874 --> 00:39:04,776
Who taught you to be so rude?

569
00:39:05,276 --> 00:39:08,112
Have you greeted me since you came in?

570
00:39:10,748 --> 00:39:11,649
Mom.

571
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:23,261
What?

572
00:39:23,862 --> 00:39:27,131
Can't I can't hug you now
that you're all grown up?

573
00:39:29,868 --> 00:39:32,337
I want to cancel the engagement
with Xiaozi from the He Corporation.

574
00:39:34,639 --> 00:39:35,807
What did you say?

575
00:39:36,741 --> 00:39:39,978
I told Xiaozi I don't love her,

576
00:39:40,545 --> 00:39:41,913
and I won't marry her.

577
00:39:42,747 --> 00:39:46,618
You call the family of He
and apologize to Xiaozi right now.

578
00:39:47,118 --> 00:39:48,486
I'll forget everything.

579
00:39:48,553 --> 00:39:49,587
That's impossible.

580
00:39:51,689 --> 00:39:53,892
In fact, I think I've already told her
what I really feel

581
00:39:53,958 --> 00:39:55,260
so I don't need to apologize to her.

582
00:39:57,328 --> 00:40:00,598
Call the He family's number for me.
I'll explain to President He myself.

583
00:40:00,665 --> 00:40:01,499
Yes.

584
00:40:03,735 --> 00:40:05,370
Ah Si, what are you doing?

585
00:40:05,436 --> 00:40:06,271
Mom.

586
00:40:07,005 --> 00:40:09,474
Listen to me, Shancai is the one I love.

587
00:40:10,241 --> 00:40:12,010
I won't marry any other woman except her.

588
00:40:12,377 --> 00:40:13,378
How dare you!

589
00:40:13,878 --> 00:40:15,680
It's not your place to decide.

590
00:40:16,514 --> 00:40:19,918
I've already chosen President He's
daughter, Xiaozi, as your future wife.

591
00:40:20,485 --> 00:40:23,288
I'm telling you, that poor woman Shancai

592
00:40:23,721 --> 00:40:26,124
won't marry into the Daoming Family,

593
00:40:26,457 --> 00:40:28,326
and she won't be able to do it
even in her next life!

594
00:40:28,559 --> 00:40:29,560
Mom!

595
00:40:30,228 --> 00:40:33,731
Why are you treating my lifetime happiness
like your business resource?

596
00:40:34,465 --> 00:40:35,900
This is what happened to my sister.

597
00:40:36,301 --> 00:40:38,069
You separated her from the man she loved,

598
00:40:38,469 --> 00:40:40,772
and you forced her to marry the son
of a tycoon in hotel industry.

599
00:40:41,072 --> 00:40:44,208
My sister never told me this,
but I always knew.

600
00:40:44,909 --> 00:40:46,611
That was the biggest regret in her heart.

601
00:40:48,813 --> 00:40:51,916
I won't be your puppet like my sister.

602
00:40:53,551 --> 00:40:55,153
Then I can tell you,

603
00:40:55,820 --> 00:40:59,023
I won't let you do anything that will
make the Daoming Family regretful.

604
00:40:59,624 --> 00:41:01,893
Your marriage to Xiaozi is final.

605
00:41:01,960 --> 00:41:04,028
If I can't even make the decision
of such things,

606
00:41:04,362 --> 00:41:06,965
how could I, Daoming Feng,
have a place in business?

607
00:41:07,031 --> 00:41:11,736
If you selfishly force me
to be together with Xiaozi,

608
00:41:12,103 --> 00:41:13,938
she will regret this for her entire life.

609
00:41:14,906 --> 00:41:17,842
And I'll be in pain forever.

610
00:41:18,476 --> 00:41:21,646
Mom, are you really going to ruin my life?

611
00:41:23,481 --> 00:41:27,785
If you marry that poor girl Shancai,
your life will be ruined.

612
00:41:28,619 --> 00:41:33,291
If our family can unite with the property
business of the He Family,

613
00:41:33,358 --> 00:41:36,127
will there be any competitors in business
after you're in charge?

614
00:41:36,861 --> 00:41:40,598
If you love me,
you should thank me for what I did.

615
00:41:40,665 --> 00:41:41,632
Mom.

616
00:41:42,734 --> 00:41:45,303
All you ever think about
is money and your business.

617
00:41:46,304 --> 00:41:50,274
Why don't you think about
how to make your son happy?

618
00:41:51,442 --> 00:41:53,778
Don't you want me to be happy?

619
00:41:56,414 --> 00:41:57,348
Mom.

620
00:41:58,216 --> 00:41:59,684
Are you really going to ruin me?

621
00:42:00,585 --> 00:42:01,619
Shut up!

622
00:42:04,222 --> 00:42:05,723
I won't let you take control of my life.

623
00:42:07,225 --> 00:42:09,060
I won't let you ruin my happiness.

624
00:42:10,395 --> 00:42:13,464
If I can, I would rather not be your son.

625
00:42:14,332 --> 00:42:16,067
I would rather not be Daoming Si!

626
00:42:17,468 --> 00:42:19,704
Stop! Ah Si!

627
00:42:23,508 --> 00:42:25,676
Gosh. Is this your house?

628
00:42:27,345 --> 00:42:28,846
It's just as big as my bathroom.

629
00:42:31,416 --> 00:42:32,950
What are you doing here?

630
00:42:33,317 --> 00:42:35,420
This is not a zoo.
There's nothing worth to look at.

631
00:42:35,520 --> 00:42:37,055
The size doesn't matter.

632
00:42:37,855 --> 00:42:40,525
How about the neighborhood?
Is it safe living by yourself?

633
00:42:41,059 --> 00:42:42,660
It's fine.

634
00:42:43,294 --> 00:42:44,996
Right, we can call Ah Si to come here.

635
00:42:45,063 --> 00:42:46,164
No.

636
00:42:46,230 --> 00:42:47,065
Why?

637
00:42:47,932 --> 00:42:49,233
No particular reason.

638
00:42:49,300 --> 00:42:52,403
Because my house is too small,
and there's no place to sit.

639
00:42:52,470 --> 00:42:54,906
You would get bored
and would want to leave soon anyway.

640
00:42:54,972 --> 00:42:56,607
So why bother inviting more people?

641
00:42:57,708 --> 00:42:59,777
Speaking of Ah Si, I don't know
what he's doing right now.

642
00:42:59,844 --> 00:43:01,312
Why didn't he go to school again today?

643
00:43:02,146 --> 00:43:04,816
Aren't things going well between him
and Xiaozi recently?

644
00:43:05,950 --> 00:43:07,952
Shancai, do you know how they are
recently?

645
00:43:08,586 --> 00:43:09,787
How would I know that?

646
00:43:13,858 --> 00:43:16,127
Just drink and stop asking her questions.

647
00:43:18,262 --> 00:43:20,998
Who could that be? I'll get the door.
You can keep drinking.

648
00:43:21,632 --> 00:43:22,600
Coming.

649
00:43:28,139 --> 00:43:29,807
Why is beer without ice so disgusting?

650
00:43:40,051 --> 00:43:42,420
I thought we'll never meet again.

651
00:43:43,254 --> 00:43:45,423
However, I have a question for you.

652
00:43:46,057 --> 00:43:47,792
What exactly did you do?

653
00:43:49,494 --> 00:43:53,431
Xiaozi's mother and Ah Si

654
00:43:53,498 --> 00:43:55,967
decided to cancel the engagement
at the same time.

655
00:43:56,467 --> 00:43:57,568
Cancel the engagement?

656
00:43:57,902 --> 00:44:02,006
When will you stop meddling
with Daoming Si's life?

657
00:44:02,640 --> 00:44:04,008
I didn't do anything.

658
00:44:05,009 --> 00:44:06,611
I knew you would say something like that.

659
00:44:07,278 --> 00:44:09,881
Your parents must be teaching you

660
00:44:10,381 --> 00:44:14,685
mean and dirty tricks
that normal people can't think of.

661
00:44:15,019 --> 00:44:18,022
Mrs. Daoming, you're damaging your dignity
with these words.

662
00:44:19,524 --> 00:44:21,692
How dare you talk to me like that.

663
00:44:22,126 --> 00:44:24,328
Do you want to lecture me
even if I am older than you?

664
00:45:54,051 --> 00:45:56,053
